	.ascii "Each time this card inflicts Battle Damage to your opponent's Life Points, you can remove up to 2 Monster Cards in your opponent's Graveyard from play. In addition, as long as this card remains face-up on the field, your opponent cannot remove any cards in either Graveyard from play.\0\0"  @ EN
