card_effect_0964:  @ @5"Possessed Dark Soul"@7 + @5"Frontier Wiseman"@7 A Fusion ...
	.ascii "@5\"Possessed Dark Soul\"@7 + @5\"Frontier Wiseman\"@7 A Fusion Summon of this monster can only be conducted with the above Fusion Material Monsters. When a Normal Spell Card is activated, negate the effect by paying 1000 Life Points. The effect of an Effect Monster that this monster destroys as a result of battle is negated.\0"  @ EN
