	.ascii "@5\"Cave Dragon\"@7 + @5\"Lesser Fiend\"@7 A Fusion Summon of this monster can only be conducted with the above Fusion Material Monsters. As long as this card remains face-up on the field, negate the effects of Flip Effect Monsters. Negate the effects of a Trap Card that targets this card and destroy it.\0"  @ EN
