card_effect_1021:  @ You can only activate this card when your opponent declares ...
	.ascii "You can only activate this card when your opponent declares an attack with a monster on his/her side of the field that has been Tribute Summoned or Set. Destroy all face-up Attack Position monsters on your opponent's side of the field and inflict 1000 points of damage to your opponent's Life Points.\0\0"  @ EN
