card_effect_1025:  @ This card cannot be Normal Summoned or Set. This monster can...
	.ascii "This card cannot be Normal Summoned or Set. This monster can only be Special Summoned by selecting 1 face-up @5\"Gradius\"@7 on your side of the field. The ATK and DEF of this card becomes the same as the ATK and DEF of the selected @5\"Gradius\"@7. If the selected @5\"Gradius\"@7 is removed from the field, destroy this card.\0"  @ EN
