card_effect_1075:  @ This card cannot be Normal Summoned or Set. This card can on...
	.ascii "This card cannot be Normal Summoned or Set. This card can only be Special Summoned from your hand or your Deck by Tributing 1 @5\"Great Dezard\"@7 that has fulfilled the condition. You can flip this card into face-down Defense Position once per turn during your Main Phase. As long as this monster remains face-up on the field, negate the activation and effects of all Spell or Trap Cards that target this card and destroy them. When this card is flipped face-up, you can Special Summon 1 Zombie-Type monster from your Graveyard in face-up Attack or Defense Position.\0"  @ EN
