	.ascii "FLIP: Special Summon 1 @5\"Poisonous Snake Token\"@7 (Reptile-Type/EARTH/3 Stars/ATK 1200/DEF 1200). When the @5\"Poisonous Snake Token\"@7 is destroyed as a result of battle, inflict 500 points of damage to your opponent's Life Points.\0\0"  @ EN
