	.ascii "By removing from play 2 WATER monsters in your Graveyard, Special Summon 1 @5\"Lekunga Token\"@7 (Plant-Type/WATER/Level 2/ATK 700/DEF 700) in Attack Position on your side of the field.\0"  @ EN
