card_effect_1273:  @ This card can only be Normal Summoned, Flip Summoned, or Spe...
	.ascii "This card can only be Normal Summoned, Flip Summoned, or Special Summoned when there is a @5\"Shooting Star Bow - Ceal\"@7 on your side of the field. Send an Equip Spell Card on your side of the field equipped to this card to the Graveyard to destroy 1 monster on your opponent's side of the field.\0\0"  @ EN
