card_effect_1283:  @ When this card inflicts Battle Damage to your opponent's Lif...
	.ascii "When this card inflicts Battle Damage to your opponent's Life Points, you can select and activate 1 of the following effects: @4€@7Return 1 card on the field to its owner's hand. @4€@7Pick up 1 card on the top of your opponent's Deck (Your opponent does not look at the card). Select the top or the bottom of the Deck and return the card there.\0\0"  @ EN
