	.ascii "You can only activate this card when there is a face-up @5\"Don Zaloog\"@7(s) on your side of the field. You can Special Summon from your hand any of the cards that include @5\"Dark Scorpion\"@7 in their card name, or are named @5\"Cliff the Trap Remover\"@7. (You can only Special Summon up to 1 card with each card name.)\0"  @ EN
