card_effect_1506:  @ Activate this card by discarding 1 LIGHT Monster Card from y...
	.ascii "Activate this card by discarding 1 LIGHT Monster Card from your hand to the Graveyard while @5\"The Sanctuary in the Sky\"@7 is on the field. Select 1 card on the field controlled by your opponent or 1 card in your opponent's hand (you can look at your opponent's hand), and send it to the Graveyard.\0\0"  @ EN
