card_effect_1646:  @ Negate the effects of your opponent's Spell Cards that desig...
	.ascii "Negate the effects of your opponent's Spell Cards that designate this card. During your Standby Phase, send this face-up card to the Graveyard to Special Summon 1 @5\"Silent Swordsman LV5\"@7 from your hand or Deck. (You cannot activate this effect the turn this card is Normal Summoned, Special Summoned, or flipped face-up.)\0\0"  @ EN
