	.ascii "This card is unaffected by your opponent's Spell Cards. If this card successfully attacks your opponent's Life Points directly, during your next Standby Phase, send this face-up card to the Graveyard to Special Summon 1 @5\"Silent Swordsman LV7\"@7 from your hand or Deck.\0\0"  @ EN
