card_effect_1739:  @ Send this face-up card on your side of the field to the Grav...
	.ascii "Send this face-up card on your side of the field to the Graveyard to Special Summon 2 Level 3 or lower Beast-Type monsters from your Deck to the field. The monsters Special Summoned in this way are destroyed during the End Phase.\0"  @ EN
