card_effect_1745:  @ When you activate this card, change all monsters on your opp...
	.ascii "When you activate this card, change all monsters on your opponent's side of the field to face-down Defense Position. While this card is face-up on the field, monsters on your opponent's side of the field cannot change their battle positions, except with a card effect. Destroy this card during your 2nd Standby Phase after activation.\0\0"  @ EN
