card_effect_1785:  @ As long as a face-down Defense Position monster(s) remains o...
	.ascii "As long as a face-down Defense Position monster(s) remains on your side of the field, a player cannot select this card as an attack target. Each time a monster on your side of the field is Flip Summoned, inflict 300 points of damage to your opponent's Life Points.\0\0"  @ EN
