card_effect_1789:  @ You can flip this card into face-down Defense Position once ...
	.ascii "You can flip this card into face-down Defense Position once per turn during your Main Phase. When this card is Flip Summoned successfully, return 1 monster on your opponent's side of the field to the owner's hand.\0"  @ EN
