	.ascii "The controller of this card cannot Normal Summon or Set. During the End Phase of the turn that a monster on your side of the field that includes @5\"B.E.S.\"@7 in its card name, or is named @5\"Big Core\"@7, is destroyed and sent to the Graveyard, you can Special Summon from your Deck 1 monster that includes @5\"B.E.S.\"@7 in its card name, or is named @5\"Big Core\"@7.\0\0"  @ EN
